==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-mmm.ogg|Audio (US)}}a

===Interjection===
'''mmm...''', '''mmmmmmm''', '''mmmmmmmmm''' etc., with as many 'm's as necessary to best convey the deliciousness of the upcoming food

# {{onomatopoeia}}: An expression used to show contentment for something, e.g., '''mmm this is a tasty pie'''

